<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Gas Token Update Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffecce;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ffaf35;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .content strong {
        color: #ffaf35;
      }
      .token-box {
        background-color: #ffbd59;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #ffbd59;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #ffaf35;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Gas Token Updated!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Your gas token has been successfully updated. Below is your new token:
        </p>
        <div class="token-box"><%= tokenId %></div>
        <p>You can use this token to access your gas allocation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help? Contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Warm regards,<br />The Gas Supply Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
